channel.title: Other people can log in but me the owner cant! Please Help
channel.description: Hey my server has been up for a while but after like a month it starts going to where other people can log into my server but me the owner cant. This has happende to me about 3 times and the only way i sloved it was tunr the server off for like a month then it magically worked again can some 1 please help me!

item.title: Other people can log in but me the owner cant! Please Help
item.dc:creator: @mister_G mister G
item.description:
@mister_G wrote:

yea it happened to me to
then i realized i had to set the server as 0.0.0.0 or 127.0.0.1
its very rare that the owner logs on with “yourname.no-ip.org”

item.title: Other people can log in but me the owner cant! Please Help
item.dc:creator: @runefreak10 runefreak10
item.description:
@runefreak10 wrote:

Is it saying “error connecting to server”? If it is, it might be because lots of player are already on and it’s making it hard for you or anyone else to get on. It might be your internet. I know this because I have the same problem. I suggest getting faster internet, maybe? That’s what I’m doing.
